Symbol.Script_3D:
if iDetlevel3D = DETLEVEL3D_OFF then end
IF gs_shadow=0 THEN SHADOW OFF
pen gs_cont_pen
if iSoilHolderType = SOILHOLDER_POLY then if iDetlevel3D <> DETLEVEL3D_DETAILED then if seg<3 then seg = 3
wink = 360/seg/2 wwa = rad * cos(wink) wwb = rad * sin(wink)
for j=1 to seg material homat prism_ 4,zzyzx, wwa-0.1,-wwb+0.1*tan(wink),15, wwa,-wwb,15, wwa,wwb,15, wwa-0.1,wwb-0.1*tan(wink),15 rotz 2*wink
material solmat prism_ 3,zzyzx-0.1, wwa-0.1,-wwb+0.1*tan(wink),15, wwa-0.1,wwb-0.1*tan(wink),0, 0,0,0 next j else if seg<3 then seg = 3
wink = 360/seg/2 wwa = rad * cos(wink) wwb = rad * sin(wink) gapHeight = min(zzyzx/10,0.02) boardHeight = (zzyzx-3*gapHeight)/4
material homat
for i=1 to 4 step 1 for j=1 to seg
prism_ 4,boardHeight, wwa-0.1,-wwb+0.1*tan(wink),15, wwa,-wwb,15, wwa,wwb,15, wwa-0.1,wwb-0.1*tan(wink),15 rotz 2*wink next j addz boardHeight+gapHeight next i
del seg*4+4
material solmat
for j=1 to seg prism_ 3, max(zzyzx-0.1,zzyzx*0.75), wwa-0.1,-wwb+0.1*tan(wink),15, wwa-0.1,wwb-0.1*tan(wink),0, 0,0,0 rotz 2*wink next j endif else ! SOILHOLDER_RECT if iDetlevel3D <> DETLEVEL3D_DETAILED then material homat prism_ 10,zzyzx, -a/2,-b/2,15, a/2,-b/2,15, a/2, b/2,15, -a/2, b/2,15, -a/2,-b/2,-1,
-a/2+0.1,-b/2+0.1,15, a/2-0.1,-b/2+0.1,15, a/2-0.1, b/2-0.1,15, -a/2+0.1, b/2-0.1,15, -a/2+0.1,-b/2+0.1,-1
material solmat add -a/2+0.1,-b/2+0.1,0 block a-0.2,b-0.2,zzyzx-0.1 del 1 else gapHeight = min(zzyzx/10,0.02) boardHeight = (zzyzx-3*gapHeight)/4 for i=1 to 4 step 1 material homat prism_ 10,boardHeight, -a/2,-b/2,15, a/2,-b/2,15, a/2, b/2,15, -a/2, b/2,15, -a/2,-b/2,-1,
-a/2+0.1,-b/2+0.1,15, a/2-0.1,-b/2+0.1,15, a/2-0.1, b/2-0.1,15, -a/2+0.1, b/2-0.1,15, -a/2+0.1,-b/2+0.1,-1
addz boardHeight+gapHeight next i del 4
material solmat
add -a/2+0.1,-b/2+0.1,0
block a-0.2,b-0.2,zzyzx-min(0.1,zzyzx/2)
del 1 endif endif
Symbol.Script_2D:
pen gs_cont_pen hotspot2 0,0 hotspot2 -a/2,-b/2 hotspot2 a/2,-b/2 hotspot2 a/2,b/2 hotspot2 -a/2,b/2
if iSoilHolderType = SOILHOLDER_POLY then wink = 360/seg/2 wwa = rad * cos(wink) wwb = rad * sin(wink)
for j=1 to seg poly2_ 4,5, wwa-0.1,-wwb+0.1*tan(wink),0, wwa,-wwb,1, wwa,wwb,0, wwa-0.1,wwb-0.1*tan(wink),1
hotspot2 wwa,-wwb hotspot2 wwa,wwb
rot2 2*wink next j
fill gs_fill_type
for j=1 to seg poly2_b 4, 2+64,gs_fill_pen,gs_back_pen, wwa,-wwb,1, wwa,wwb,1, 0,0,1, wwa,-wwb,-1 rot2 2*wink next j else rect2 -a/2,-b/2,a/2,b/2 rect2 -a/2+0.1,-b/2+0.1,a/2-0.1,b/2-0.1
fill gs_fill_type poly2_b 5, 2+64,gs_fill_pen,gs_back_pen, -a/2,-b/2,1, a/2,-b/2,1, a/2, b/2,1, -a/2, b/2,1, -a/2,-b/2,-1 endif
Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: iDetlevel3D DETLEVEL3D_DETAILED = 1 DETLEVEL3D_SIMPLE = 2 DETLEVEL3D_OFF = 3
SOILHOLDER_RECT = 1 SOILHOLDER_POLY = 2
dim stDetlevel3D[3] stDetlevel3D[1] = `Детальный` stDetlevel3D[2] = `Простой` stDetlevel3D[3] = `Откл.`
dim stSoilHolderType[2] stSoilHolderType[1] = `Прямоугольный` stSoilHolderType[2] = `Многоугольный`
rad=a/2
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
values "zzyzx" range (0.01, ) values "seg" RANGE [3,)
values{2} "iDetlevel3D" DETLEVEL3D_DETAILED, stDetlevel3D[1], DETLEVEL3D_SIMPLE, stDetlevel3D[2], DETLEVEL3D_OFF, stDetlevel3D[3]
values{2} "iSoilHolderType" SOILHOLDER_RECT, stSoilHolderType[1], SOILHOLDER_POLY, stSoilHolderType[2]
if gs_cont_pen=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=4 if gs_fill_pen=0 then parameters gs_fill_pen=91
if iSoilHolderType = SOILHOLDER_POLY then if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "B" then A = B parameters A = A else B = A parameters B = B endif endif
if iSoilHolderType <> SOILHOLDER_POLY then hideparameter "seg" lock "seg" endif
! ============================================================================= ! UI ! =============================================================================
values "gs_ui_current_page" 1
Symbol.Script_UI:
TABID_ROOT = -1 TABID_TYPE = 1
ui_current_page gs_ui_current_page
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! *** Page 1 *** !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! ui_page TABID_TYPE, TABID_ROOT, `Тип Ящика для Грунта`, "uiTab_Style_flat(1)"
pageStartY = 5
ui_infield{3} "iSoilHolderType", 0, pageStartY, 444, 260, 1, 1, ! ui_SoilHoldTypes.png 2, 1, 132, 162, 128, 128, 1, stSoilHolderType[1], SOILHOLDER_RECT, 2, stSoilHolderType[2], SOILHOLDER_POLY
